'''Gáius Juleis Káisar''' (Latinisks: GAIVS•IVLIVS•CAESAR) (Hawimenoþs 13, 102/100 F.X.-Aústramenoþs 15, 44 F.X.) was Rumons reiki-manna, konsul, jah ana-mahtja. Is ga-dailiþ waúrþanona þata tiuhans andja Rumons Þiudawaíhts jah ur-rists Rumons Reikjis. In 60 F.X., Káisar, Krassus, jah Pompeis skapjand ''Triumviratus Primus'' ("Fruma Hansaþridjins") faúr kindeins aízasokeins bi ''Populares'' ("ansts þiudōs") deþos þata and-weihun bi ''Optimates'' ("batists manna") inna Rumons Þiudawaíhtstaþs, hindar ija was Katon Jūhizan jah Kikeron. Is bláuþs Galljins was us-fulljand in 51 F.X., bi ize is ana-filhand fruman dis-sita Brita-landis afar timrjand brugja ufar Rein. Ƕan Gallisk Wigana andiþs, in 49 þiudawaíhtstaþs fra-qiþaidēdun ina af-giban is harjis jah qums aftra Rumái. Káisar un-weriþ jah and-saƕt is aízasokeins miþ qiss  "''alea iacta est''" - "waúrpil ist waírpiþ", jah fōr Italjái. Gaggans Rumons aírþa ni-witodeigaba, ana-stôdejands aftumist Gáuja-Wigan Rumons Þiudawaíhts. In 44 F.X. ana Eidus Aústramēnōþ (''Martiī Īdus''), is was maúrþriþs bi Þiudawaíhtstaþ. Is Ga-láubeins was Rumons Haíþneins. Is was mikila-áuaháims Aúktaweinins.

