==Libáins jah runs-gatwo==   
Juleis Káisar ga-baúrans Áurelja Kotta (''Aurelia Cotta'') jah Gáius Juleis Káisar III (''Gaius Julius Caesar III''). Is swistrjus wēsun Julja Káisaris Minaúr (''Julia Caesaris Minor'') jah Julja Káisaris Majaúr (''Julia Caesaris Major''). Is was áina-baúr. Is fadreins in-sahtun wisan fadreina Áinaíaïs jah gudinjō lubōns Wēnáus. Seins fadar diwans ƕan is was 16. Is áuaháims was Gáius Marius, konsul at stiks mēlis jah fijands was Lukius Kaúrnelius Sulla. Káisar was namnjand ''Flamen Dialis'' (Háuhs-Guja) Iowái in 85 F.X. Is liugaíþs Kaúrnelja Sinnilla (''Cornelia Cinnilla'') spráutō afar. In 75 F.X., Káisar was fra-hinaþ bi Kilikisks sáiws-þiufōs jah halōþ fra-hunþans. Is habáida fraþi wulþridomis, bi-hlahida ija, ''"Scis quis sum?"'' "finþis ƕas-uh ik im?" qaþ is. Ƕan sáiws-þiufans ana-báuþ tigjus silubr skattōs, Káisar qaþ gibai fimf tigjus. Ƕan dulg was galþ, afariddja sáiws-þiufans miþ flutan, jah fra-hinaþ ija is slitida ize halos jah báuþ ija wisan hahans, ga-háit tawida sáiws-þiufōs nam swa saldra. Is aftra ga-laíþ harjis deþs miþ bandjōs ''Auxilia'' ("hilpa") in Asia stáutan dis-sita fram áusta.

Ana is qam-aftra Rumái, is was ga-waliþs harjis tribuns. Is was ga-waliþs qáistor faúr 69 F.X. Iddja fulla-fahjan is qáistoraskips in Hispanja. Und þate þar, ga-môteiþ ga-digis Alaíksandráus Mikilan, ƕan at is alds, Alaíksandrus bláuþida managists mēris midjun-gards. Káisar gaígrōt þata is láistōda leitils ni-waíhts. Ana is qam-aftra in 67, liugiþ Pompeia. In 63, is ga-walida swa Frumists-Gudja (''Pontifex Maximus'') ƕar bi-bugida jah ga-jiukiþs. Afar fulla-fahjands swe práitor in 62, ráidida waldan Hispanja. Bláuþida twa neƕ-bi kunja jah ga-teih ''imperator'' (káisar) bi is dráuhtōs. Swe ''imperator'', Káisar qam-aftra Rumái jah was gibans ''laurus'' (hroþ). Is wilida wisan konsul, aþþan habáidēdi dis-wisan is harjis jah inn-gaggai Ruma sundro-baúrgja. Fraíhniþ Þiudawaíhtstaþ wisan bi-nah standan ''in absentia'', aþþan Katōn láugniþs ita. Is waleiþ konsulskips.

==Wigan in Gallja==
58–50 F.X.

Káisar was naúh-þanuþ in dulgs. Aþþan þar was skatts wisan skapiþs swa ragineis, Káisar habáida fidwor laígaíona undar ina. Sama dáila Galljins wēsun kunþs wisan un-þwasts. Sama Rumōs Gallisks tráustona habaida wisans bláuþiþs bi ija fijōnds in Badwis Magetobriga, miþ hilpa Þiudiskis kunja. Káisar brukiþs sah swe wigs stigqan is bláuþs þana-máis in Gallja. Badwis Magetobriga was aftumists badwa ana midumái ''Haedui'' (Háidans) wiþra ''Suebi'' (Swebans), ''Sequani'' (Seqanans), jah ''Arverni'' (Arbaírnans). Rumoneis faúrhtida þō kunja manwidēdeina ga-gaggan sunþs, neƕiza Italjái. Káisar þan-uh bláuþjands þō kunja.

Naúrþa-aúst kunja du-ginnodēdun arman ija silbona, aþþan Káisar bláuþida ija dáila-mēl. Und-þate áin is laígaíona iddja bláuþ in kunja in faírra naúrþ. In 56, Ruma was in agliþa jah ragini Káisaris was qums andeis. Ita was ana-niwida faúr aljis fimf jēra. In sumar 55, Káisar faírinōda Britisk hilpands fijonds, ''Veneti'' (Wenetans) Brittanjōs. Káisar iddja Brita-landis aþþan habáida Galljins faúr wintrus. Is aftra ga-laíþ afar-jer batiza manwus jah miþ mikiliza harjis. Un-lēþs harbists faíriniþ us-walteins in Gallja, skapida Káisar bi-leiþiþ jah ni-áiw qam-aftra Brita-landis.

[[𐍆𐌴𐌹𐌻𐌰:Siege-alesia-vercingetorix-jules-cesar.jpg|thumbnail|left|Waírkiggetaúreiks at-wairpiþ is wepna at fotjus Juleis Káisaris]]

Und þate Káisar was in Brita-land, Julja, qēnaís Pompeis, dáu in barn-baúrþs in 54. Krassus was af-slah in Badwis Karrái in 53, jah Pompeis un-werida liugan mikila-nifts Káisaris. Pompeis aírzeis ga-láubeins in Káisar, ''triumviratus'' dis-was. In 52, ''Vercingetorix'' (Wairkiggetaureiks) tiuhans mikiliza us-walteins in Gallja, ga-widans Gallisks kunja jah bláuþjands Káisar manags mēla ufar. Aþþan Káisar bi spedistin ga-jiukiþs in Badwis Alesia. Gallja was nu undar Rumons waldufni. Bi Plutarkus, in-sahtiþ harjis weihans swa manags swe þridja miljō mannans miþþane Wigan, áina miljō diwans, aljis miljō was ga-þiwans. Rumoneis uf-hnáiwjands 300 kunja jah fra-qistjands 800 baúrgjans. Sah raþjô ni-wēsi glaggwus. Afar Wigan, ga-mēlida ''Commentarii De Bello Gallico'' (Raþjōns ana Gallisk Wigan).

==Reikeins-Wigan==
50-45 F.X.

In 50, Pompeis biudida Káisar dis-wisan is harjis jah qam aftra Rumái duþþē is runs swa ragineis was andiþs. Káisar þagkida þata is wēsi wrikans iþ inn-gaggida Ruma inuh harjis. Pompeis faírinōns miþ at-leweins. Ana Aftuma Jiuleis 10, 49, Káisar iddja Rubikon aƕa, miþ þatáine laígaíon jah ana-stôdjands reikeins-wigan. Ana gaggans Rubikon, Káisar þata-qaþ is walisa Krek kaúmaúdja bokareis Menander, ''Ἀνερρίφθω κύβος'' "waúrpil ist waírpiþ." Qiss fruma at-áugeiþ in “Ἀρρηφόρος” (''Arrephoros,'') (aíþþáu Swigl-Mawi) swē þata-qaþ in ''Deipnosophistae'', ''Bokōs 13''. Plutarkus spilliþ þata þō waúrda was qiþans in Krekiska:

"Ἑλληνιστὶ πρὸς τοὺς παρόντας ἐκβοήσας, 'Ἀνερρίφθω κύβος', [anerriphtho kybos] διεβίβαζε τὸν στρατόν."

"Is ga-baírhtida miþ hlūþs stibna im ƕa was at-satida 'Lēt waúrpil waírpiþ', jah tiuh is harjis þaírh."

Pompeis jah Þiudawaíhtstaþ unþa-þliuh sunþa, habans leitils traúaíns in is niujis drauhtōs. Pompeis ni-wileiþ weihan, jabá Káisar habida þatáine is Þreis-taíhunda laígaíon miþ ina. Káisar afargaggans Pompeis, sa-e unþa-þliuh faúr Káisar mahteigs was fra-hinþan ina. afargaggida jah bláuþans Pomeis in Kreka-land in Wiudamenoþs in 48, at ''Dyrrhachium'' (Dyrrakion), Káisar spediza þata jer, bláuþida aftra at Farsalus. Káisar afargaggans Pompeis Aígwptáus, ƕar Pomeis af-slah at handjus Ptolomeiōs XIII. Káisar was modags bi sah, qiþans hlūþaba, "''Romae Consul fuit!''" "Is was Konsul Rumōs!" ga-nimands sah miþ tagra. Is þan-uh habáida banans Pomeiōs af-slahans.       

[[𐍆𐌴𐌹𐌻𐌰:Cleopatra and Caesar by Jean-Leon-Gerome.jpg|thumbnail|left|Kleopatra jah Juleis Káisar]]

Káisar þan-uh waírþida blandans miþ Aígwpteins reikeins-wigan ana midumái barn farao jah is swistar/qēns/miþ-faúra-maþleis Kleopatra. Káisar bláuþida juggs faraons drauhtōs at Badwa Neiláus in laggateins 47, jah skapida Kleopatra Farao. Ptlolomeis XIV was áuk skapjands niujis miþ-faúra-maþleis. Káisar bilibans in Aígwptus þandē Grasmenoþs. In 48, is was aftra ga-waliþs ''Dictator'', miþ áin jēr runs. Afar fra-qimands fruma menoþs in 47, Káisar iddja Midjis Aústa, ƕar af-slah þiudans Pontáus. Is sigis was spráutô bláuþida þata bi-láikida faúra-sigona Pompeios. Káisar ga-weisôns fram 25–27 Blomamenoþs 47 in Tarsus, ƕar ga-môtida þiudawaíhtstaþeins stutja, jah Kasseis bi sah ƕeila, wilida ina dáuþs. Þaþrō, iddja Afar-landis us-niman aftumists dáilōs Pompeiōs þiudawaíhtstaþeins stutja. Is spráutô ga-geigans sigis ufar Katōn, ƕas bi þan-uh sis silbin us-qimans.

Afar sah sigis, is was ga-waliþs ''Dictator'' faúr aljis taíhun jera. Sunjus Pompeios unþa-þliuh faúr Hispanja. Káisar afargaggans ins jah bláuþida ins in Badwa Mundōs in Aústramenoþs 45. Is was aftra ga-waliþs imma þridja jah fidurþa runōs swe konsul in 46 jah 45.

==Konsulskips jah Dáuþus==
45-44 F.X.
[[𐍆𐌴𐌹𐌻𐌰:Karl Theodor von Piloty Murder of Caesar 1865.jpg|thumbnail|left|Þiudawaíhtstaþs þreih Káisar]]

Ƕan Káisar qam-aftra Rumins, Þiudawaíhtstaþs giband is Rumons hrōþa faúr is sigis ufar Aígwptus, Gallja, Farnakēs II Pontáus, jah Juba I Numidjōs, máis alja ufar is Rumons fijonds. Ƕan Arsinaúaí IV Aígwptáus, runans þaírh baúrgs, þiuda luband ija jah wagiþs arman. Gamans was swah haldida, 2,000 mannans, 200 aíƕōs jah 20 elefans haifstiþs dáuþáu. Agliþa dis-taúrnans jah þatáinē andiþs áuk twa þiuda hunslida at Akrs Maris.  Is aftra-ga-tewiþs Rumons dagatala sustaím. Káisar us-tiuh ita miþ Aígwpteins dagatala. Ist ibna-leiks 365.25 dagōs jer, bi áukida hláupa-daga ana andeis Hroþimenoþ ibna fidwor jera. Us-lukniþ ana 1 Aftuma Jiuleis 45 F.X. Ist neƕa nu Xristeins dagatala jah frums Ga-sateins baúrgs (''Ab urbe condita'') dagatala. Is stiurida waldufni jah biwida aftra-ana-stodeins Karþagonis jah Kaúrinþis. In Fanimenoþs 44, áins menoþs faúr is maúrþr, is was nimans ''vitae dicator'' (af-mahts faúr libáins) jah menoþ ''Quintilis'' was aftra-nimans ''Iulius'' (Hawimenoþs) in is sweriþa. Neƕa andi is libáins, is skapjands wigan wiþra Parþa-land Reiki.

Ana Eidus Aústramenoþ, -44, Káisar qimans Þiudawaíhts. Tilleis Simbar jah aljis ga-rinnand bi Káisar. Káisar af-skiubida áuk Simbar ana-habida ahlsans jah þinsida páida Káisaris. Káisar áuhiōþs Simbara, ''"Ista quidem vis est!"'' ("Duƕe, sah ist háifsts!"). Þata samo Kaska tiuh is kneifs jah stigqida at is hnakka. Is qēþi ''"Casca, carnifex te, quid facis?"'' "Kaska, þu wargs, ƕe is þu táujands?" swe bi Plutarkus. Kaska, agands, hrops in Krekisks, "Hilp, broþar!" ''("ἀδελφέ, βοήθει!", "adelphe, boethei!").'' Káisar us-dáudida unþa-þliuhan áuk ga-huliþs in bloþ, sliupida jah driusida, mannans fastand stikands ina. Is was stikands 23 ƕeilōs. Satida is páida ufar is háubiþ swa ni-áinshun sēƕeina ina diw. Aftumists waúrda Káisaris habaidēdeina Krekisks qiss ''"καὶ σύ, τέκνον?, Kai su, teknon?"'' "Þuk swah, barn?" Habaidēdi ni-waíhts aíþþáu ''"Et tu, Brute?"'', fram Wiljahilms Skaskpeirē ''"Juleis Káisar"''. Brutus þliuhida ga-timrjō, qiþida þiudōs, "Þiuda Rumōs, sijum aftra freis!" Twái menoþs afar is dáuþus, eis-tagla-staírno ƕarbōda ana Blomamenoþs 18, "Sidus lulium" namnjand ita afar ija dáuþs faúr-stasseis, ƕas was nu gudiþs.

==Leikeins hiwi jah sundro libáins==
Káisar habaidēdi epilepsja aíþþáu habaidēdi háubiþ-saíra. Rumons spill-stasseis Suetoneis qaþ Káisar swe "tals, ibns fill jah lagjōs, miþ skarps swarts áugona."           

==Bi-Leiþans==
Juleis Káisar ist ga-kunnans swe managists mērs faúr-stasseis in spill. Is þata qiþano, "lēt waúrpil waírpiþ" ist naúh-þanuþ qiþans in Italja, swē ''"Il dado è tratto"''. Is bōkōs ''Commentarii de Bello Gallico'' ist naúh-þanuþ wisans ana-kunnans hina dag bi manags þiudōs bi midjun-gards.

